'I don't think I was thinking at that
 time,' she said. 'I felt ashamed. I felt guilty. I didn't want to come 
forward because I didn't want my family to know.'

Julie Ann Rojas, who was Gries then-girlfriend, testified that she was with Van and Esparza the night Ramirez died.

